What books have you read lately?

332
00:25:20.690 --> 00:25:21.920
A Hundred Thousand Whys.

333
00:25:21.920 --> 00:25:23.030
What?

334
00:25:23.030 --> 00:25:24.790
A Hundred Thousand Whys.

335
00:25:24.790 --> 00:25:26.790
Will you please articulate?

336
00:25:28.070 --> 00:25:30.350
A Hundred Thousand Whys.

337
00:25:30.350 --> 00:25:31.900
What's the matter?

338
00:25:31.900 --> 00:25:34.200
The astronomy and geography volume.

339
00:25:34.200 --> 00:25:35.400
Don't laugh.

340
00:25:35.400 --> 00:25:39.650
Ye Wenjie clearly evaded your question.

341
00:25:39.650 --> 00:25:41.550
Did she not want to answer it? Or she couldn't answer it?

342
00:25:41.550 --> 00:25:42.830
How am I supposed to know?

343
00:25:42.830 --> 00:25:46.110
That's why we need to keep investigating Ye Wenjie.

344
00:25:52.340 --> 00:25:56.860
- Hello? 
 - <i>Are you responsible for looking into Wei Cheng?</i>

345
00:26:16.140 --> 00:26:20.310
Captain Shi, this is indeed against the rules,

346
00:26:20.310 --> 00:26:24.960
