347
00:26:24.960 --> 00:26:27.450
Why is he doing calculations here?

348
00:26:27.450 --> 00:26:29.600
This guy's pretty weird.

349
00:26:29.600 --> 00:26:32.600
He brought a pile of infosheets and a computer here, and said he wanted to report a crime,

350
00:26:32.600 --> 00:26:34.960
